{"tid":2114600,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國據報尋求日本協助建5G　NEC富士通或成供應商","createTime":"2020-07-19T03:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T03:29:12.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0541632a850536222b0aeeb0ee880527b87edfca","tid":2114600,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:17:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538626-20200719.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538626-20200719.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Se3jk6qONbDe%2BTgec%2FNeBz%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=3266d7ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538626-20200719.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0ca12c3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538626-20200719.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n《日經新聞》報道，英國政府已經向日本尋求協助，參與建設5G網絡。<br />\n<br />\n英國上星期宣布禁用華為建設5G，報道表示，英國官員星期四曾經與日本官員在東京會面，英國可能會以日本的NEC與富士通，作為替代供應商。消息指，英國政府正努力引入新的設備供應商，維持在5G建設上的競爭力。<br />\n<br />\n英國駐日本大使館、日本內閣官方長官辦公室，以及NEC與富士通都未有就事件回應。"},{"pid":"8b52a467fa64b0dead2d81cfdc1ddb317e40f06d","tid":2114600,"uid":322766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:18:36.000Z","msg":"快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7e0de16151373c35b8b6bcffe89e7397a96223","tid":2114600,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:24:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e008b540b80664a8b4f28c967d323cc0f9c56dc4","tid":2114600,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T03:29:12.000Z","msg":"點解係都唔用Nokia？"}]}